<section id="gido-bot-terms" class="about-us">
    <div class="container">
        <h2>📜 Gido Bot Terms of Use</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>🤖 **Instant Activation** - Once Gido Bot joins your server, it’s ready to serve! No extra setup needed. Just use the commands and start interacting!</li>
            <li>🛠️ **Bot Permissions** - Gido Bot requires certain permissions to function properly (like managing messages, playing music, and more). Make sure it has the right roles!</li>
            <li>🧠 **Customizable Settings** - Tailor Gido Bot’s behavior to your server’s needs. You can adjust the prefix, responses, and even its music preferences!</li>
            <li>🔍 **Monitoring Activity** - Gido Bot might track user activity for features like ranking or moderation. But don’t worry, privacy is a top priority! 🚨</li>
            <li>🚪 **Auto Leave on Inactivity** - If no one is active in a voice channel, Gido Bot will say goodbye and exit the voice channel server . 💤</li>
            <li>🚨 **Obey the Rules** - Gido Bot will follow server rules and won’t engage in any disruptive behavior. However, if misused, it could get muted or kicked! 😱</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
